	   <tr><td colspan=2>What do bards need?<br><br>In this Order Cha,Agi,Dex,Sta.<br><br>The Bards Most important function is his songs, without the bards songs he is nothing more than a Rogue.<br>Charisma,for those who dont know, is the primary focus for bards, because it helps the song play more Efficiently. Dexterity is used in like with Agility,because they help the abilities that bards can get later on. Agility is important because without it you are hit harder and more often,Stamina For a bards built in regeneration. Normally 2 pts per tick with a high stamina it can reach 3 or 4 points per tick. I also believe Str is important but i did not list it because it is not important enough to survive in battle.<br><br>As for Equipment. Early on basicly get what you want Leather, Patchwork a Trusty blade. when you get into your teens you should start thinking about Charisma increasing items more, along with Dexterity and Agility. Different piecs of lambent armor do different things, but all pieces contain Charisma Increasers.<br><br>If you are a Bard, PLEASE make him agnostic before it is too late. agnostics have an easier time with everything, and with Evl Masks (Iksar Hide, Deception) that have effects of illiusion Iksar and Dark elf, you can pretty much enter any city. you can gain faction with every City, Including Ogguk, Grobb, Neriak, Cabilis, with ease. why do you all think that enchanters are agnostic as well? because they get illusions for every race.<br>Being a godless race gives evil cities no reason to attack you, if you are illusioned like one of them.<br><br>anyway i hope this helps.<br><br>Gremandor Twilitesiren<br>(34 bard Bristlebane, 31 bard Nameless)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
