	   <tr><td colspan=2>you must remember MOST NOT ALL bard songs last for "ticks". each tick is 3 secs r so i think. songs take bout 3 secs to start so you can see the effects (ex. Your wounds begin to heal). now each song lasts 3 ticks i think (9 secs for the  Einsteins here). so that allows you to twist 3-4 songs. i've never seen someone able to twist 5 songs, but i would reject to that if im in their grp  =)  anyways to accomplish twisting you must start song 1, wait for the effect to show on your screen then immediately push 2 twice. this stops song 1 and starts song 2. now wait for effect (should be 3 secs or so) and hit 3 twice and so on...<br><br>once you get the timing down, you'll between to twist when your kiting then eventually in battle while using other abilities like we bards do  =)  wit alittle practice, you can achieve ALMOST anything  =P<br><br>Taamas Starsinger<br>38th Season<br>House of Wargoth<br>Saryrn<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
